Bodapp Limited has introduced a new online boda boda hailing service offering passenger and parcel transit to individuals and corporate clients in Nairobi. Our sole purpose is to serve our customers by giving them a safer, convenient and trustworthy experience with our bodaboda taxi and parcel delivery services. Everything with us is top notch, from the boda boda s to the service itself, whether you re a customer or an employee we ll be there for you and your needs, said Bodapp Limited CEO Robin Kungu.The Kenyan owned company which commenced operations in August 2016 currently has a database of over 200 riders.